-- RusHydro to Invest $7.1 Billion in 2012-2014, Interfax Reports
-- B y   T o r r e y   C l a r k
-- 2011-12-30T08:45:38Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-30/rushydro-to-invest-7-1-billion-in-2012-2014-interfax-reports.html
OAO RusHydro plans to invest 227
billion rubles ($7.1 billion) in 2012 through 2014, Interfax
reported, citing an unidentified person with knowledge of the
program.  The plan for 2012 was cut by 14 percent to 88.9 billion
rubles and for 2013 by 18 percent to 78.1 billion rubles,
Interfax said. The amounts were discussed this week at a meeting
with Deputy Prime Minister  Igor Sechin  this year, the news
service reported.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Torrey Clark at 
 tclark8@bloomberg.net  